Daly_City.Duboce and Church station: Duboce and Church (Church and Duboce for the J Church line) is a light rail stop on the Muni Metro J Church and N Judah lines, located in the Duboce Triangle neighborhood of San Francisco, California. Just east of the station, the two lines enter the Market Street Subway. The station originally opened with the 22 Fillmore line (now a trolleybus line) in 1895.
